URL = https://openeconomylog.org


=Description=

Open Economy Log is a tool that helps people work together to build up a picture of what's happening in their local economy and to help each other find resources that originate locally. It works by letting people openly log the resources they use and where those resources come from. Open Economy Log is a new project on its trial run so feedback is welcome.
 
 
